            {"id": "D3", "text": "Reports are available which include internal and external leavers and the completeness of these reports can be demonstrated."},
            {"id": "D4", "text": "Access rights of workforce including a link between users and their user IDs / accounts on systems are known and documented to support the locking / removal of all access for leavers."},
            {"id": "D5", "text": "A documented process is in place initiate the locking / removal of all access for leavers."},
            {"id": "D6", "text": "Mechanisms are in place to ensure that the locking / removal of all access for leavers is being successfully completed."},
            {"id": "D7", "text": "An emergency leaver process is in place to lock / remove the critical access for leavers in a reliable way within 24 hours if required."},
