            {"id": "E3", "text": "has been locked / removed in a timely manner (screenshots from systems showing accounts as locked / removed with date when this was implemented)."},
            {"id": "E2", "text": "Evidence that the network access for a small sample of external leavers (3-5) from the report obtained as"},
