            {"id": "E5", "text": "Document covering the process / mechanism for locking the access for leavers with confirmation that it covers the (types of) systems selected in the sample."},
            {"id": "E6", "text": "Evidence (1 leaver for each system included in the sample with access to it - mix of internal and external users - 5 samples in total) that there is a robust and systematic (process) link between the event of identifying a leaver and the actual and timely removal of access for the sampled system. Details on the QA process (if existing) which ensures that all removals have been fully completed."},
            {"id": "E7", "text": "Documented emergency leaver process and 1 sample demonstrating that the implemented process meets the target timelines for removing access."},
